<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.6">
<l>viṇṇellāṅ kēṭka vaḻutiṭṭā yuṉvāyil</l>
<l rend="indent">virumpi yataṉaināṉ nōkki</l>
<l>maṇṇellāṅ kaṇṭeṉ maṉattuḷḷē yañci</l>
<l rend="indent">matucūta ṉēyeṉ ṟaṟintēṉ</l>
<l>puṇṇētu millaiyuṉ kātu maṟiyum</l>
<l rend="indent">poṟuttiṟaip pōtiru nampi</l>
<l>kaṇṇāveṉ kārmuki lēkaṭal vaṇṇā</l>
<l rend="indent">kāvala ṉēmulai yuṇāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who cried so that all the heavens heard,</l>
<l>I adoringly looked inside your mouth [and] seeing all the worlds,</l>
<l>feared in my mind - I knew [then that you are] Madhusūdhana.</l>
<l>There [will be] no wound whatsoever,</l>
<l>[but] your ears will be injured.</l>
<l>Sit patiently for just a moment, Nampi! Krsna!</l>
<l>My Dark Cloud! Ocean-hued One! Protector! Drink [from my] breast!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
